title: Sports: The Gathering
description: The KAJ starts off by picking their Starting 5 Disney Princesses to fill out an NBA team (00:28), then it's time for some updates: Friendly Banter (4:18), Mental Health (33:32), DJ Magic the Gathering (41:10), The Challenge (53:18), The Pupdate (1:00:59), and A Goosebumps Book Report (1:09:59). Later, Katie, Ashley and Jay have intel on Every. Single. Major. Sport. (1:35:55). Because you know what, bud? This is a sports podcast, that is about sports. Famously.
